{
  "video_id": "RD07GkmM2fc",
  "title": "Mike Biddle: We can recycle plastic",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 18259.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a garbage man."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "And you might find it interesting that I became a garbage man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "because I absolutely hate waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 26260.0,
      "text": "I hope, within the next 10 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26260.0,
      "end_time": 28260.0,
      "text": "to change the way you think"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "about a lot of the stuff in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;d like to start at the very beginning."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "Think back when you were just a kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36260.0,
      "text": "How did look at the stuff in your life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36260.0,
      "end_time": 40260.0,
      "text": "Perhaps it was like these toddler rules:"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40260.0,
      "end_time": 43260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s my stuff if I saw it first."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "The entire pile is my stuff if I&#39;m building something."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "The more stuff that&#39;s mine, the better."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "And of course, it&#39;s your stuff if it&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "Well after spending about 20 years in the recycling industry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 59260.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s become pretty clear to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59260.0,
      "end_time": 61260.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t necessarily leave these toddler rules behind"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61260.0,
      "end_time": 63260.0,
      "text": "as we develop into adults."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "And let me tell you why I have that perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "Because each and every day"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "at our recycling plants around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 72260.0,
      "text": "we handle about one million pounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "of people&#39;s discarded stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Now a million pounds a day sounds like a lot of stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 79260.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s a tiny drop of the durable goods"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 79260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "that are disposed each and every year around the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "well less than one percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "In fact, the United Nations estimates"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "that there&#39;s about 85 billion pounds a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 89260.0,
      "text": "of electronics waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89260.0,
      "end_time": 91260.0,
      "text": "that gets discarded around the world each and every year --"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s one of the most rapidly growing parts of our waste stream."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 97260.0,
      "text": "And if you throw in other durable goods like automobiles and so forth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97260.0,
      "end_time": 99260.0,
      "text": "that number well more than doubles."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "And of course, the more developed the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "the bigger these mountains."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "Now when you see these mountains,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 107260.0,
      "text": "most people think of garbage."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107260.0,
      "end_time": 109260.0,
      "text": "We see above-ground mines."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 109260.0,
      "end_time": 112260.0,
      "text": "And the reason we see mines is because there&#39;s a lot of valuable raw materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 115260.0,
      "text": "that went into making all of this stuff in the first place."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s becoming increasingly important"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "that we figure out how to extract these raw materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 123260.0,
      "text": "from these extremely complicated waste streams."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 123260.0,
      "end_time": 125260.0,
      "text": "Because as we&#39;ve heard all week at TED,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 125260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "the world&#39;s getting to be a smaller place with more people in it"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "text": "who want more and more stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 130258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133260.0,
      "text": "And of course, they want the toys and the tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 133260.0,
      "end_time": 135260.0,
      "text": "that many of us take for granted."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 135260.0,
      "end_time": 138260.0,
      "text": "And what goes into making those toys and tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 138260.0,
      "end_time": 140260.0,
      "text": "that we use every single day?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 140260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s mostly many types of plastics and many types of metals."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 146260.0,
      "text": "And the metals, we typically get"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 146260.0,
      "end_time": 148260.0,
      "text": "from ore that we mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 148260.0,
      "end_time": 150260.0,
      "text": "in ever widening mines"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 150260.0,
      "end_time": 152260.0,
      "text": "and ever deepening mines around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 152260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "And the plastics, we get from oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "which we go to more remote locations"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 160260.0,
      "text": "and drill ever deeper wells to extract."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 160260.0,
      "end_time": 162260.0,
      "text": "And these practices have"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 165260.0,
      "text": "significant economic and environmental implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re already starting to see today."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 171260.0,
      "text": "The good news is we are starting to recover materials from our end-of-life stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 171260.0,
      "end_time": 173260.0,
      "text": "and starting to recycle our end-of-life stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 173260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "particularly in regions of the world like here in Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 179260.0,
      "text": "that have recycling policies in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181260.0,
      "text": "that require that this stuff be recycled"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 181260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "in a responsible manner."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 185260.0,
      "text": "Most of what&#39;s extracted from our end-of-life stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188260.0,
      "text": "if it makes it to a recycler, are the metals."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190260.0,
      "text": "To put that in perspective --"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190260.0,
      "end_time": 192260.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m using steel as a proxy here for metals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 192260.0,
      "end_time": 194260.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the most common metal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 194260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "if your stuff makes it to a recycler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "probably over 90 percent of the metals"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 201260.0,
      "text": "are going to be recovered and reused for another purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 201260.0,
      "end_time": 203260.0,
      "text": "Plastics are a whole other story:"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 203260.0,
      "end_time": 205260.0,
      "text": "well less than 10 percent are recovered."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 205260.0,
      "end_time": 207260.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s more like five percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 207260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "Most of it&#39;s incinerated or landfilled."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 211260.0,
      "text": "Now most people think that&#39;s because plastics are a throw-away material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 211260.0,
      "end_time": 213260.0,
      "text": "have very little value."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "But actually, plastics are several times more valuable than steel."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s more plastics produced and consumed"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "around the world on a volume basis"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 222260.0,
      "text": "every year than steel."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 222260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "So why is such a plentiful and valuable material"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 227260.0,
      "text": "not recovered at anywhere near the rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 227260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "of the less valuable material?"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 231260.0,
      "text": "Well it&#39;s predominantly because"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 231260.0,
      "end_time": 233260.0,
      "text": "metals are very easy to recycle"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 233260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "from other materials and from one another."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "They have very different densities."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "They have different electrical and magnetic properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "And they even have different colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s very easy for either humans or machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 246260.0,
      "text": "to separate these metals"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 246260.0,
      "end_time": 248260.0,
      "text": "from one another and from other materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 248260.0,
      "end_time": 252260.0,
      "text": "Plastics have overlapping densities over a very narrow range."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 252260.0,
      "end_time": 254260.0,
      "text": "They have either identical or very similar"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 254260.0,
      "end_time": 256260.0,
      "text": "electrical and magnetic properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 256260.0,
      "end_time": 258260.0,
      "text": "And any plastic can be any color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "as you probably well know."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "So the traditional ways of separating materials"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "just simply don&#39;t work for plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 266260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "Another consequence of metals being so easy to recycle by humans"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 272260.0,
      "text": "is that a lot of our stuff from the developed world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 275260.0,
      "text": "and sadly to say, particularly from the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 275260.0,
      "end_time": 278260.0,
      "text": "where we don&#39;t have any recycling policies in place like here in Europe --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 278260.0,
      "end_time": 280260.0,
      "text": "finds its way to developing countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 280260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "for low-cost recycling."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "People, for as little as a dollar a day, pick through our stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "They extract what they can, which is mostly the metals --"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290260.0,
      "text": "circuit boards and so forth --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 290260.0,
      "end_time": 292260.0,
      "text": "and they leave behind mostly what they can&#39;t recover,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 292260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "which is, again, mostly the plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 298260.0,
      "text": "Or they burn the plastics to get to the metals"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 298260.0,
      "end_time": 300260.0,
      "text": "in burn houses like you see here."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 300260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "And they extract the metals by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 304260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "Now while this may be the low-economic-cost solution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "this is certainly not the low-environmental"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 312260.0,
      "text": "or human health-and-safety solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 312260.0,
      "end_time": 315260.0,
      "text": "I call this environmental arbitrage."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 315260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not fair, it&#39;s not safe"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s not sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 321260.0,
      "end_time": 323260.0,
      "text": "Now because the plastics are so plentiful --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 323260.0,
      "end_time": 325260.0,
      "text": "and by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 325260.0,
      "end_time": 327260.0,
      "text": "those other methods don&#39;t lead to the recovery of plastics, obviously --"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 327260.0,
      "end_time": 329260.0,
      "text": "but people do try to recover the plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 329260.0,
      "end_time": 331260.0,
      "text": "This is just one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 331260.0,
      "end_time": 333260.0,
      "text": "This is a photo I took standing on the rooftops"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 333260.0,
      "end_time": 336260.0,
      "text": "of one of the largest slums in the world in Mumbai, India."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 336260.0,
      "end_time": 338260.0,
      "text": "They store the plastics on the roofs."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 338260.0,
      "end_time": 341260.0,
      "text": "They bring them below those roofs into small workshops like these,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 341260.0,
      "end_time": 344260.0,
      "text": "and people try very hard to separate the plastics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 344260.0,
      "end_time": 346260.0,
      "text": "by color, by shape, by feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 346260.0,
      "end_time": 348260.0,
      "text": "by any technique they can."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 348260.0,
      "end_time": 350260.0,
      "text": "And sometimes they&#39;ll resort to what&#39;s known as the \"burn and sniff\" technique"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 350260.0,
      "end_time": 352260.0,
      "text": "where they&#39;ll burn the plastic and smell the fumes"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 352260.0,
      "end_time": 355260.0,
      "text": "to try to determine the type of plastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 355260.0,
      "end_time": 358260.0,
      "text": "None of these techniques result in any amount of recycling"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 358260.0,
      "end_time": 360260.0,
      "text": "in any significant way."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 360260.0,
      "end_time": 362260.0,
      "text": "And by the way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 362260.0,
      "end_time": 364260.0,
      "text": "please don&#39;t try this technique at home."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 364260.0,
      "end_time": 367260.0,
      "text": "So what are we to do about this space-age material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 367260.0,
      "end_time": 370260.0,
      "text": "at least what we used to call a space-aged material, these plastics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 370260.0,
      "end_time": 373260.0,
      "text": "Well I certainly believe that it&#39;s far too valuable and far too abundant"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 375260.0,
      "text": "to keep putting back in the ground"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 375260.0,
      "end_time": 377260.0,
      "text": "or certainly send up in smoke."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 377260.0,
      "end_time": 380260.0,
      "text": "So about 20 years ago, I literally started in my garage tinkering around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 380260.0,
      "end_time": 382260.0,
      "text": "trying to figure out how to separate"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 382260.0,
      "end_time": 384260.0,
      "text": "these very similar materials from each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 384260.0,
      "end_time": 387260.0,
      "text": "and eventually enlisted a lot of my friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 387260.0,
      "end_time": 390260.0,
      "text": "in the mining world actually, and in the plastics world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 393260.0,
      "text": "and we started going around to mining laboratories around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 393260.0,
      "end_time": 396260.0,
      "text": "Because after all, we&#39;re doing above-ground mining."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 396260.0,
      "end_time": 398260.0,
      "text": "And we eventually broke the code."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 398260.0,
      "end_time": 400260.0,
      "text": "This is the last frontier of recycling."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 400260.0,
      "end_time": 402260.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the last major material"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 402260.0,
      "end_time": 404260.0,
      "text": "to be recovered in any significant amount on the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 404260.0,
      "end_time": 406260.0,
      "text": "And we finally figured out how to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 406260.0,
      "end_time": 408260.0,
      "text": "And in the process, we started recreating"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 408260.0,
      "end_time": 410260.0,
      "text": "how the plastics industry makes plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 410260.0,
      "end_time": 412260.0,
      "text": "The traditional way to make plastics"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 412260.0,
      "end_time": 414260.0,
      "text": "is with oil or petrochemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 414260.0,
      "end_time": 417260.0,
      "text": "You breakdown the molecules, you recombine them in very specific ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 417260.0,
      "end_time": 420260.0,
      "text": "to make all the wonderful plastics that we enjoy each and every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 420260.0,
      "end_time": 423260.0,
      "text": "We said, there&#39;s got to be a more sustainable way to make plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 423260.0,
      "end_time": 426260.0,
      "text": "And not just sustainable from an environmental standpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 426260.0,
      "end_time": 429260.0,
      "text": "sustainable from an economic standpoint as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 429260.0,
      "end_time": 431260.0,
      "text": "Well a good place to start is with waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 431260.0,
      "end_time": 433260.0,
      "text": "It certainly doesn&#39;t cost as much as oil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 433260.0,
      "end_time": 435260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s plentiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 435260.0,
      "end_time": 437260.0,
      "text": "as I hope that you&#39;ve been able to see from the photographs."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 437260.0,
      "end_time": 439260.0,
      "text": "And because we&#39;re not breaking down the plastic into molecules"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 439260.0,
      "end_time": 441260.0,
      "text": "and recombining them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 441260.0,
      "end_time": 444260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re using a mining approach to extract the materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 444260.0,
      "end_time": 446260.0,
      "text": "We have significantly lower capital costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 446260.0,
      "end_time": 448260.0,
      "text": "in our plant equipment."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 448260.0,
      "end_time": 450260.0,
      "text": "We have enormous energy savings."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 450260.0,
      "end_time": 452260.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know how many other projects on the planet right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 452260.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "can save 80 to 90 percent of the energy"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 455260.0,
      "end_time": 457260.0,
      "text": "compared to making something the traditional way."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 457260.0,
      "end_time": 459260.0,
      "text": "And instead of plopping down several hundred million dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 459260.0,
      "end_time": 461260.0,
      "text": "to build a chemical plant"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 464260.0,
      "text": "that will only make one type of plastic for its entire life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 464260.0,
      "end_time": 467260.0,
      "text": "our plants can make any type of plastic we feed them."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 467260.0,
      "end_time": 469260.0,
      "text": "And we make a drop-in replacement"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 469260.0,
      "end_time": 471260.0,
      "text": "for that plastic that&#39;s made from petrochemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 471260.0,
      "end_time": 473260.0,
      "text": "Our customers get to enjoy"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 473260.0,
      "end_time": 475260.0,
      "text": "huge CO2 savings."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 475260.0,
      "end_time": 477260.0,
      "text": "They get to close the loop with their products."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 477260.0,
      "end_time": 479260.0,
      "text": "And they get to make more sustainable products."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 479260.0,
      "end_time": 481260.0,
      "text": "In the short time period I have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 481260.0,
      "end_time": 484260.0,
      "text": "I want to show you a little bit of a sense about how we do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 484260.0,
      "end_time": 487260.0,
      "text": "It starts with metal recyclers who shred our stuff into very small bits."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 487260.0,
      "end_time": 489260.0,
      "text": "They recover the metals"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 489260.0,
      "end_time": 491260.0,
      "text": "and leave behind what&#39;s called shredder residue -- it&#39;s their waste --"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 491260.0,
      "end_time": 493260.0,
      "text": "a very complex mixture of materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 495260.0,
      "text": "but predominantly plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 495260.0,
      "end_time": 497260.0,
      "text": "We take out the things that aren&#39;t plastics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 497260.0,
      "end_time": 500260.0,
      "text": "such as the metals they missed, carpeting, foam, rubber,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 500260.0,
      "end_time": 503260.0,
      "text": "wood, glass, paper, you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 503260.0,
      "end_time": 505260.0,
      "text": "Even an occasional dead animal, unfortunately."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 505260.0,
      "end_time": 508260.0,
      "text": "And it goes in the first part of our process here, which is more like traditional recycling."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 508260.0,
      "end_time": 510260.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re sieving the material, we&#39;re using magnets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 510260.0,
      "end_time": 512260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re using air classification."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 512260.0,
      "end_time": 514260.0,
      "text": "It looks like the Willy Wonka factory at this point."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 514260.0,
      "end_time": 517260.0,
      "text": "At the end of this process, we have a mixed plastic composite:"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 517260.0,
      "end_time": 519260.0,
      "text": "many different types of plastics"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 519260.0,
      "end_time": 521260.0,
      "text": "and many different grades of plastics."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 521260.0,
      "end_time": 523260.0,
      "text": "This goes into the more sophisticated part of our process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 523260.0,
      "end_time": 527260.0,
      "text": "and the really hard work, multi-step separation process begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 527260.0,
      "end_time": 530260.0,
      "text": "We grind the plastic down to about the size of your small fingernail."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 530260.0,
      "end_time": 532260.0,
      "text": "We use a very highly automated process"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 532260.0,
      "end_time": 534260.0,
      "text": "to sort those plastics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 534260.0,
      "end_time": 536260.0,
      "text": "not only by type, but by grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 536260.0,
      "end_time": 538260.0,
      "text": "And out the end of that part of the process"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 538260.0,
      "end_time": 540260.0,
      "text": "come little flakes of plastic:"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 542260.0,
      "text": "one type, one grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 542260.0,
      "end_time": 545260.0,
      "text": "We then use optical sorting to color sort this material."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 545260.0,
      "end_time": 548260.0,
      "text": "We blend it in 50,000-lb. blending silos."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 548260.0,
      "end_time": 551260.0,
      "text": "We push that material to extruders where we melt it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 551260.0,
      "end_time": 553260.0,
      "text": "push it through small die holes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 553260.0,
      "end_time": 555260.0,
      "text": "make spaghetti-like plastic strands."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 555260.0,
      "end_time": 557260.0,
      "text": "And we chop those strands"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 557260.0,
      "end_time": 559260.0,
      "text": "into what are called pellets."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 559260.0,
      "end_time": 563260.0,
      "text": "And this becomes the currency of the plastics industry."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 563260.0,
      "end_time": 566260.0,
      "text": "This is the same material"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 566260.0,
      "end_time": 568260.0,
      "text": "that you would get from oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 568260.0,
      "end_time": 570260.0,
      "text": "And today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 570260.0,
      "end_time": 573260.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re producing it from your old stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 573260.0,
      "end_time": 576260.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going right back into your new stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 576260.0,
      "end_time": 585260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 585260.0,
      "end_time": 587260.0,
      "text": "So now, instead of your stuff ending up"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 587260.0,
      "end_time": 589260.0,
      "text": "on a hillside in a developing country"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 589260.0,
      "end_time": 591260.0,
      "text": "or literally going up in smoke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 591260.0,
      "end_time": 593260.0,
      "text": "you can find your old stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 593260.0,
      "end_time": 596260.0,
      "text": "back on top of your desk in new products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 596260.0,
      "end_time": 598260.0,
      "text": "in your office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 598260.0,
      "end_time": 600260.0,
      "text": "or back at work in your home."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 600260.0,
      "end_time": 602260.0,
      "text": "And these are just a few examples"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 602260.0,
      "end_time": 604260.0,
      "text": "of companies that are buying our plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 604260.0,
      "end_time": 606260.0,
      "text": "replacing virgin plastic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 606260.0,
      "end_time": 608260.0,
      "text": "to make their new products."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 608260.0,
      "end_time": 610260.0,
      "text": "So I hope I&#39;ve changed the way you look at"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 610260.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "at least some of the stuff in your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 612260.0,
      "end_time": 614260.0,
      "text": "We took our clues from mother nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 614260.0,
      "end_time": 616260.0,
      "text": "Mother nature wastes very little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 616260.0,
      "end_time": 618260.0,
      "text": "reuses practically everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 618260.0,
      "end_time": 621260.0,
      "text": "And I hope that you stop looking at yourself as a consumer --"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 621260.0,
      "end_time": 624260.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a label I&#39;ve always hated my entire life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 624260.0,
      "end_time": 628260.0,
      "text": "and think of yourself as just using resources in one form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 628260.0,
      "end_time": 630260.0,
      "text": "until they can be transformed to another form"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 630260.0,
      "end_time": 632260.0,
      "text": "for another use later in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 632260.0,
      "end_time": 635260.0,
      "text": "And finally, I hope you agree with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 635260.0,
      "end_time": 638260.0,
      "text": "to change that last toddler rule just a little bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 638260.0,
      "end_time": 641260.0,
      "text": "to: \"If it&#39;s broken, it&#39;s my stuff.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 641260.0,
      "end_time": 643260.0,
      "text": "Thank you for your time."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 643260.0,
      "end_time": 652260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}